    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the car starts up without issue and handles basic commutes well, though the suspension is beginning to show its age. Externally, there are some noticeable paint chips and minor scuffs consistent with regular use, and the interior shows some wear on the upholstery. It is a solid, honest car that provides dependable transportation for those who prioritize utility over perfection.",
