    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and mechanical integrity. This selection offers a refined driving experience, balancing robust performance with exceptional value. Thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for quality and reliability, this offering represents an ideal acquisition for the discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-caliber motorcar.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
